                                    used files and, as such, we will refer to these files as cookies hereinafter.</p>
                                     
                                    <p>Cookies used for any of the following purposes are exempt from the provisions laid down in Article 22.2 of
                                    the LSSI-CE:<br><ul>
                                     
                                    <li> Only to allow communication between the user’s equipment and the network.</li>
